org.magnos.trie

Class PerfectHashMap<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.magnos.trie.PerfectHashMap<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The value type.

    public class PerfectHashMap<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A simple map implementation where the keys are integers and are used as direct indices into the map. The minimum and maximum key values define the size of the underlying table and thus should be as near to each other as possible.
    Author:
    Philip Diffenderfer
